Okay, first of all,
you look magical and amazing,

00:29.360 --> 00:30.650
but I don't understand
what you're saying.

00:30.680 --> 00:32.750
So if you want to make it in this land,

00:32.790 --> 00:34.800
you really need to speak English.

00:34.830 --> 00:37.360
How's your first day of school?
It's grand.

00:37.380 --> 00:38.690
Hey, Irish.

00:40.220 --> 00:42.750
Wait. Other people can see you?

00:43.850 --> 00:45.560
But only because you let them see you.

00:45.580 --> 00:47.880
That's right.

00:47.910 --> 00:49.100
I've thought about it a lot,

00:49.160 --> 00:50.680
and I know what I want as my first wish.

00:50.720 --> 00:52.040
Your magical race,

00:52.070 --> 00:53.580
they make my favorite cereal,
Lucky Charms.

00:53.580 --> 00:54.970
I really wish that you

00:54.990 --> 00:56.670
would make me a box of Lucky Charms

00:56.780 --> 00:59.240
with all marshmallows. You're in luck.

