Lucky the Leprechaun
happens to be my cousin.

01:01.760 --> 01:04.150
And he lives two toadstools down.

01:04.180 --> 01:05.680
Thank you.

01:05.720 --> 01:07.700
Though I don't understand
most of what you just said.

01:09.140 --> 01:10.780
Work on it.

