** For a girl like you **

29:05.920 --> 29:10.220
** To come into my life **

29:10.240 --> 29:13.060
** I've been waiting **

29:13.130 --> 29:15.400
** For a girl like you **

29:15.430 --> 29:19.870
** And a love that will survive **

29:19.920 --> 29:22.250
** Yeah, waiting **

29:22.310 --> 29:25.130
** For a girl like you **

29:25.160 --> 29:30.370
** To come into my life... **

