32:18.730 --> 32:21.610
Uh, excuse me, sweetie.

32:21.630 --> 32:24.110
Susan, we have a problem.

32:24.230 --> 32:27.510
You're a candidate for office,
so campaign law says

32:27.550 --> 32:30.780
