opponent equal time.

32:30.910 --> 32:32.760
What new opponent?

32:34.160 --> 32:35.630
Hi, folks.

32:35.680 --> 32:37.950
My name is Burt Hummel,
and I want to be your congressman.

32:37.950 --> 32:40.520
Now, Sue Sylvester,
she's gotten a lot of mileage,

32:40.550 --> 32:42.460
coming on this show and
scaring you into thinking

32:42.500 --> 32:44.250
